#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:14
msgid "A body that is controlled by the 2D physics engine."
msgstr "由2D物理引擎控制的物体。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"This node implements simulated 2D physics. You do not control a "
"RigidBody2D directly. Instead you apply forces to it (gravity, impulses, "
"etc.) and the physics simulation calculates the resulting movement based "
"on its mass, friction, and other physical properties."
msgstr ""
"该节点实现模拟的2D物理。您不能直接控制 "
"``RigidBody2D``。取而代之的是对它施加力（重力、冲力等），然后物理模拟根据其质量、摩擦力、和其他物理性质，来计算结果的运动。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:21
msgid ""
"A RigidBody2D has 4 behavior :ref:`mode "
"<class_RigidBody2D_property_mode>`\\ s: Rigid, Static, Character, and "
"Kinematic."
msgstr ""
"``RigidBody2D`` 具有以下4种行为 :ref:`mode "
"<class_RigidBody2D_property_mode>`：刚体、静态、角色和运动。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Note:** You should not change a RigidBody2D's ``position`` or "
"``linear_velocity`` every frame or even very often. If you need to "
"directly affect the body's state, use :ref:`_integrate_forces "
"<class_RigidBody2D_method__integrate_forces>`, which allows you to "
"directly access the physics state."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：您不应每帧甚至经常更改 ``RigidBody2D`` 的 ``position`` 或 ``linear_velocity`` "
"。如果您需要直接影响物体的状态，请使用 :ref:`_integrate_forces "
"<class_RigidBody2D_method__integrate_forces>`，它允许您直接访问物理状态。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:25
msgid ""
"Please also keep in mind that physics bodies manage their own transform "
"which overwrites the ones you set. So any direct or indirect "
"transformation (including scaling of the node or its parent) will be "
"visible in the editor only, and immediately reset at runtime."
msgstr "还请记住，物理物体管理它们自己的变换，该变换会覆盖您设置的变换。因此，任何直接或间接转换（包括节点或其父级的缩放）仅在编辑器中可见，并在运行时中立即重置。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:27
msgid ""
"If you need to override the default physics behavior or add a "
"transformation at runtime, you can write a custom force integration. See "
":ref:`custom_integrator <class_RigidBody2D_property_custom_integrator>`."
msgstr ""
"如果需要覆盖默认的物理行为，或在运行时中添加转换，则您可以编写自定义合力。请参阅 :ref:`custom_integrator "
"<class_RigidBody2D_property_custom_integrator>`。"

