#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:306
msgid ""
"Continuous collision detection tries to predict where a moving body will "
"collide instead of moving it and correcting its movement after collision."
" Continuous collision detection is slower, but more precise and misses "
"fewer collisions with small, fast-moving objects. Raycasting and "
"shapecasting methods are available. See :ref:`CCDMode "
"<enum_RigidBody2D_CCDMode>` for details."
msgstr ""
"连续碰撞检测试图预测移动物体将发生碰撞的位置，而不是移动它并在碰撞后校正其运动。连续碰撞检测速度较慢，但精度更高，并且与快速移动的小型物体的碰撞次数更少。可以使用射线投射和形状投射方法。有关详细信息，请参见"
" :ref:`CCDMode <enum_RigidBody2D_CCDMode>`。"

