msgstr "应用一个方向性冲力而不影响旋转。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:511
msgid ""
"void **apply_impulse** **(** :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` offset, "
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` impulse **)**"
msgstr ""
"void **apply_impulse** **(** :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` offset, "
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` impulse **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:513
msgid ""
"Applies a positioned impulse to the body. An impulse is time-independent!"
" Applying an impulse every frame would result in a framerate-dependent "
"force. For this reason it should only be used when simulating one-time "
"impacts (use the \"_force\" functions otherwise). The position uses the "
"rotation of the global coordinate system, but is centered at the object's"
" origin."
msgstr ""
"向物体施加一个定位冲力。冲力与时间无关！每帧施加一个冲力将产生一个依赖帧速率的力。因此，仅在模拟一次性冲击时才应使用它（否则请使用 "
"``_force`` 函数）。该位置使用全局坐标系的旋转，但以对象的原点为中心。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:519
msgid ""
"void **apply_torque_impulse** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` torque "
"**)**"
msgstr ""
"void **apply_torque_impulse** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` torque "
"**)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:521
msgid "Applies a rotational impulse to the body."
msgstr "向物体施加旋转冲力。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:527
msgid ":ref:`Array <class_Array>` **get_colliding_bodies** **(** **)** const"
msgstr ":ref:`Array <class_Array>` **get_colliding_bodies** **(** **)** const"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:529
msgid ""
"Returns a list of the bodies colliding with this one. Use "
":ref:`contacts_reported <class_RigidBody2D_property_contacts_reported>` "
"to set the maximum number reported. You must also set "
":ref:`contact_monitor <class_RigidBody2D_property_contact_monitor>` to "
"``true``."
msgstr ""
"返回与该物体碰撞的物体的列表。使用 :ref:`contacts_reported "
"<class_RigidBody2D_property_contacts_reported>` 设置报告的最大数量。您还必须将 "
":ref:`contact_monitor <class_RigidBody2D_property_contact_monitor>` 设置为 "
"``true``。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:531
msgid ""
"**Note:** The result of this test is not immediate after moving objects. "
"For performance, list of collisions is updated once per frame and before "
"the physics step. Consider using signals instead."
msgstr "**注意**：移动物体后，该测试的结果不是立即产生的。为了提高性能，重叠列表每帧和物理步骤之前更新一次。考虑改用信号。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:537
msgid ""
"void **set_axis_velocity** **(** :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` "
"axis_velocity **)**"
msgstr ""
"void **set_axis_velocity** **(** :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` "
"axis_velocity **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:539
msgid ""
"Sets the body's velocity on the given axis. The velocity in the given "
"vector axis will be set as the given vector length. This is useful for "
"jumping behavior."
msgstr "设置物体在给定轴上的速度。给定向量轴上的速度将设置为给定向量长度。这对于跳跃行为很有用。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:545
msgid ""
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **test_motion** **(** :ref:`Vector2 "
"<class_Vector2>` motion, :ref:`bool <class_bool>` infinite_inertia=true, "
":ref:`float <class_float>` margin=0.08, :ref:`Physics2DTestMotionResult "
"<class_Physics2DTestMotionResult>` result=null **)**"
msgstr ""
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **test_motion** **(** :ref:`Vector2 "
"<class_Vector2>` motion, :ref:`bool <class_bool>` infinite_inertia=true, "
":ref:`float <class_float>` margin=0.08, :ref:`Physics2DTestMotionResult "
"<class_Physics2DTestMotionResult>` result=null **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody2d.rst:547
msgid ""
"Returns ``true`` if a collision would result from moving in the given "
"vector. ``margin`` increases the size of the shapes involved in the "
"collision detection, and ``result`` is an object of type "
":ref:`Physics2DTestMotionResult <class_Physics2DTestMotionResult>`, which"
" contains additional information about the collision (should there be "
"one)."
msgstr ""
"如果在给定向量中移动会导致碰撞，则返回 ``true``。``margin`` 增加了碰撞检测中涉及的形状的大小，而 ``result`` "
"是类型为 :ref:`Physics2DTestMotionResult <class_Physics2DTestMotionResult>` "
"的对象，其中包含有关碰撞（应该有一个 ）的其他信息。"

